item.title: CVE-2020-6256|2024-08-04T08:55:22.211Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20master%20data%20governance
item.description: SAP Master Data Governance, versions - 748, 749, 750, 751, 752, 800, 801, 802, 803, 804, allows users to display change request details without having required authorizations, due to Missing Authorization Check.
